data.description: Don't miss your chance for maintenance free living! This PRE-INSPECTED 2B, 2B, 2 car garage townhome is ready for new owners! You'll appreciate open concept living on the main floor with tons of natural light, new flooring, plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen, a full bath & a walk in pantry. Ready to get your grill on this summer? Step outside onto your small back patio with no rear neighbors just lots of shade from the mature trees. Upstairs you'll find (2) bedrooms with soaring ceilings & large closets, another full bath, and the convenient laundry room w/ extra storage. Two car garage has plenty of storage room for your toys and the HOA covers exterior maintenance, snow removal & lawn care.  NEW Windows, washer, refrigerator, & dishwasher. Conveniently located near Standing Bear Lake Recreation Area, schools, theaters, grocery, restaurants, and so much more. Don't wait to see this one, schedule your showing today!
